# ─── Environment Variables ─────────────────────────────────────────
# This project currently does NOT require any custom environment variables.
#
# It relies exclusively on Next.js built-in `process.env.NODE_ENV`
# (set automatically to `development`, `production`, or `test`).
#
# ─── Future Configuration ─────────────────────────────────────────
# If you add OAuth, a database, or external APIs, document them here:
#
#   # Google OAuth (optional)
#   GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
#   GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=
#
#   # Database (optional)
#   DATABASE_URL=
#
#   # External API (optional)
#   API_KEY=
